1565
01:09:02,990 --> 01:09:05,840
three year growth period--

1566
01:09:05,840 --> 01:09:12,050
I'm going to simply take
powers of this factor 1 plus r.

1567
01:09:12,050 --> 01:09:19,100
So $1 in year 0 is going
