01:09:36,479 --> 01:09:38,069
It's called the growth rate.

1573
01:09:38,069 --> 01:09:39,747
It's called the cost of capital.

1574
01:09:39,747 --> 01:09:41,580
It's called the opportunity
cost of capital.

1575
01:09:41,580 --> 01:09:44,100
John Maynard Keynes
