1576
01:09:44,100 --> 01:09:46,005
There are tons of
names for this quantity

1577
01:09:46,005 --> 01:09:51,602
but the basic idea is it's the
reverse of the exchange rates

1578
01:09:51,602 --> 01:09:54,060
